STATE
v.
Paul Dewayne CUMMINGS. No. 1A05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 15, 2005. William N. Farrell, Jr., Senior Deputy Attorney General, Ben David, District Attorney, for State of NC.

AMENDED

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 11th day of August 2005 by Defendant for Extension of Time for Court Reporter to Prepare the Transcript:
